=== TEST 1: receive
--- config
    location /t {
        content_by_lua '
            local sock, err = ngx.req.socket()
            sock.receive("l")
        ';
    }
--- request
    POST /t
--- more_headers: Content-Length: 1024
--- response_body_like: 500 Internal Server Error
--- error_code: 500
--- error_log
bad argument #1 to 'receive' (table expected, got string)



